Name: NASCAR Xfinity Racing Series
Title: The Chilango 150
Desc: The NASCAR Xfinity Series heads to Mexico for The Chilango 150 at the Autódromo Hermanos Rodríguez.
LongDescription: The NASCAR Xfinity Series heads to Mexico for The Chilango 150 at the Autódromo Hermanos Rodríguez. After a four-year stint from 2005 to 2008, stock car racing returns to Mexico City in support of the Cup Series' first excursion to the course.
